<p>Fresh back from CES, John and Dave share their thoughts and trends about the show. Then it&#39;s on to answering your questions with topics including sharing Contacts with iCloud, solving erroneous Safari suggestions, the efficacy of smart chargers, the future of AirPlay and more! Download today, press play and enjoy (all while learning!).</p>
